{"tid":1284864,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[急 區議會DQ書] send email去選管會無用，仲要諗其他方法！","createTime":"2019-07-04T10:44:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T09:04:39.000Z","uid":31174,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"1576a10a566a3c5234517ac066be23a6c1a640f6","tid":1284864,"uid":31174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T10:44:29.000Z","msg":"1. 以選管會慣例，proposed guidelines好少因爲申述而改，衰啲講句，佢出黎做諮詢都係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>假諮詢</strong></span>黎，因為法例要求先跟住做，但其實<strong>根本唔會改</strong><br />\n<br />\n2. 選管會收到我地啲有關guidelines嘅申述，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">係唔會作任何回覆</span></strong>，最多覆你一封email話：「我地收到啦，多謝你關注。」<br />\n<br />\n利申：之前都試過表達意見，但都淨係收到呢封acknowledgment。佢係唔會對於我地嘅意見作私下或公開嘅回覆。<br />\n<br />\n平時選區劃界會有一本書公開所有口頭同書面申述，但guidelines就唔會有呢本書仔。佢過咗諮詢期一兩個月就直接出本final guidelines，唔會回應我地嘅申述。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">所以email要照send，但同時要諗其他方向迫選管會回應！！！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\nP.S. email記得唔好用template！重組句子完先好記出去！"},{"pid":"4c935e428674a7166d3977c69b4e84d7ef501fdf","tid":1284864,"uid":31174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T10:44:45.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">我冇野講</code></pre>"},{"pid":"5308d019715c6895374bc3a108bb230dc8765d01","tid":1284864,"uid":64953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T10:46:18.000Z","msg":"711截止？<br />\n一人兩實體信(中英文)塞滿佢信箱？<br />\n另外再加fax?"},{"pid":"02a274c3ffbcd81bc7ef7142492d93b41cbaa45b","tid":1284864,"uid":31174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5308d019715c6895374bc3a108bb230dc8765d01","tid":1284864,"uid":64953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T10:46:18.000Z","msg":"711截止？<br />\n一人兩實體信(中英文)塞滿佢信箱？<br />\n另外再加fax?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T10:48:17.000Z","msg":"7月10截止<br />\n<br />\n塞爆當然要啦<br />\n但有咩計可以逼到馮燁出黎講野"},{"pid":"8533b0bf41b54abc76a43675730cd99ec087bc51","tid":1284864,"uid":31174,"like":0,